comments: Davis (LAL) legally contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Len (SAC) moves into Davis's (LAL) space in the post, but the contact is marginal.
Haliburton (SAC) makes contact with Davis's (LAL) arm that affects his ability to get to the pass.
Len (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Monk (LAL) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Westbrook (LAL) loses control of the rebound, and is the last to touch the ball, before it goes OOB.
Davis (SAC) makes contact to the arm of James (LAL) on the drive that affects his SQBR.
James (LAL) makes contact to Hield's (SAC) body as he tries to defend around the screen and the contact affects his FOM.
James (LAL) lowers his shoulder into Bagley III's (SAC) body at the end of his drive and dislodges him from his guarding position.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bagley III (SAC) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Anthony (LAL) makes marginal contact with Metu's (SAC) arm while cutting through the lane, but does not affect his ability to defend.
Len (SAC) makes body contact with Davis (LAL) that affects his SQBR during his shot attempt near the rim.
Westbrook (LAL) places his off-arm against Fox (SAC), who is falling off-balance when Westbrook releases from the contact.
James (LAL) clamps and holds Hield's (SAC) arm and affects his ability to pursue the loose ball.
Len (SAC) makes contact with James' (LAL) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Bagley III (SAC) makes marginal contact to the body of James (LAL) at the end of the drive that does not affect his SQBR.
The game clock stops at 00:24.7 and the shot clock is incorrectly shut off.  Play should have been stopped to adjust the clocks for the 0.7 second differential.
Thompson (SAC) makes contact with James' (LAL) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Thompson (SAC) is last to make contact with ball before it goes OOB. LAL maintains possession of the ball.
Hield (SAC) makes contact with Davis (LAL) arm during his finish at the rim.
Bradley (LAL) makes marginal body and arm contact with Fox (SAC) during his driving shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
Fox (SAC) makes contact with Westbrook (LAL) body that affects his play at the basket.
Westbrook (LAL) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
Davis (LAL) commits a clear path foul on Hield (SAC).
